       ["str"],
       true,
       "itertools.starmap.__doc__.__class__.__name__.__eq__('str') == True — starmap's docstring is a plain Python str; __doc__.__class__.__name__ is 'str'; str.__eq__('str') returns True; new to extra198"]
    - [starmap_bases_object,
